snippet.title: Gods Eater Burst - PSP - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out now all the features of the game Gods Eater Burst on PSP only! Freely customize weapons, guns, bullets, and shields to increase your chances of survival, and your characters outfits to create your very own hero. Transform your God Arc to predator form to gain a temporary boost in stats and special bullets allowing you to launch a super powerful attack. And so much more...

Gods Eater Burst will hit Europe on the 18th of March 2011 on PSP™.

Enroll with the God Eaters to Protect mankind on http://www.facebook.com/GodEaterBurst or get more information on your local http://www.namcobandaigames.eu website
